select distinct Orden from allearter where  1=1  order by Orden asc
select distinct Klasse from allearter where  1=1  order by Klasse asc

select distinct Raekke from allearter where  1=1  order by Raekke asc

select distinct Orden from allearter where  1=1  order by Orden asc
select distinct Orden from allearter where Orden like "o%" and  1=1  order by Orden asc
select distinct Orden from allearter where  1=1  order by Orden asc
select distinct Klasse from allearter where  1=1  order by Klasse asc
select distinct Slaegt from allearter where  1=1  order by Slaegt asc

select distinct Raekke from allearter where Klasse="Bryopsida"

Artsgruppe_dk like "%Bufo viridis%") and Dansk="Ja" order by Videnskabeligt_navn

select distinct Familie from allearter where Familie like "Carabidae%" and  1=1  order by Familie asc
select distinct Orden from allearter where Familie="Carabidae"
select distinct Klasse from allearter where Orden="Coleoptera"
select distinct Raekke from allearter where Klasse="Insecta"
select distinct Rige from allearter where Raekke="Arthropoda"
select ID, Videnskabeligt_navn, Autor, Dansk_navn, Familie, Familie_dk, Orden, Orden_dk, Artsgruppe, Artsgruppe_dk, Slaegt_dk, Referencenavn, Reference_aar, Referencetekst, Den_danske_roedliste, Fredede_arter, Dansk, Synonymer, Synonymer_dk from allearter where 1=1  and Rige="Animalia" and Raekke="Arthropoda" and Klasse="Insecta" and Orden="Coleoptera" and Familie="Carabidae" and Dansk="Ja" order by Videnskabeligt_navn
select ID, Videnskabeligt_navn, Autor, Dansk_navn, Familie, Familie_dk, Orden, Orden_dk, Artsgruppe, Artsgruppe_dk, Slaegt_dk, Referencenavn, Reference_aar, Referencetekst, Den_danske_roedliste, Fredede_arter, Dansk, Synonymer, Synonymer_dk from allearter where 1=1  and (Rige like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Rige_dk like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Raekke like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Raekke_dk like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Underraekke like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Underraekke_dk like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or

select distinct Raekke from allearter where Klasse="Hepaticopsida"
select distinct Rige from allearter where Raekke="Hepatophyta"
select ID, Videnskabeligt_navn, Autor, Dansk_navn, Familie, Familie_dk, Orden, Orden_dk, Artsgruppe, Artsgruppe_dk, Slaegt_dk, Referencenavn, Reference_aar, Referencetekst, Den_danske_roedliste, Fredede_arter, Dansk, Synonymer, Synonymer_dk from allearter where 1=1  and (Rige like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Rige_dk like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Raekke like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Raekke_dk like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Underraekke like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or Underraekke_dk like "%Abax parallelepipedus%" or

Artsgruppe_dk like "%Abax parallelepipedus%") and Dansk="Ja" order by Videnskabeligt_navn

select distinct Rige from allearter where Raekke="Cnidaria"
select ID, Videnskabeligt_navn, Autor, Dansk_navn, Familie, Familie_dk, Orden, Orden_dk, Artsgruppe, Artsgruppe_dk, Slaegt_dk, Referencenavn, Reference_aar, Referencetekst, Den_danske_roedliste, Fredede_arter, Dansk, Synonymer, Synonymer_dk from allearter where 1=1  and Rige="Animalia" and Raekke="Cnidaria" and Klasse="Anthozoa" and Dansk="Ja" order by Videnskabeligt_navn
select ID, Videnskabeligt_navn, Autor, Dansk_navn, Familie, Familie_dk, Orden, Orden_dk, Artsgruppe, Artsgruppe_dk, Slaegt_dk, Referencenavn, Reference_aar, Referencetekst, Den_danske_roedliste, Fredede_arter, Dansk, Synonymer, Synonymer_dk from allearter where 1=1  and Raekke="Oomycota" and Dansk="Ja" order by Videnskabeligt_navn

select distinct Familie from allearter where  1=1  order by Familie asc
select distinct Orden from allearter where Familie="Leuctridae"
select distinct Klasse from allearter where Orden="Plecoptera"
select distinct Raekke from allearter where Klasse="Insecta"
select distinct Rige from allearter where Raekke="Arthropoda"

Artsgruppe_dk like "%høg%") order by Videnskabeligt_navn

Orden like "%miris%" or Orden_dk like "%miris%" or Underorden like "%miris%" or Underorden_dk like "%miris%" or Infraorden like "%miris%" or Infraorden_dk like "%miris%" or Overfamilie like "%miris%" or Overfamilie_dk like "%miris%" or Familie like "%miris%" or Familie_dk like "%miris%" or Underfamilie like "%miris%" or 
Underfamilie_dk like "%miris%" or Tribus like "%miris%" or Tribus_dk like "%miris%" or Slaegt like "%miris%" or Slaegt_dk like "%miris%" or Videnskabeligt_navn like "%miris%" or Dansk_navn like "%miris%" or Synonymer like "%miris%" or Synonymer_dk like "%miris%" or Artsgruppe like "%miris%" or  
Artsgruppe_dk like "%miris%") and Dansk="Ja" order by Videnskabeligt_navn

Artsgruppe_dk like "%vikke%") order by Videnskabeligt_navn

select Videnskabeligt_navn from allearter where Dansk_navn="Blågrå jordugle"
select ID, Videnskabeligt_navn, Autor, Dansk_navn, Familie, Familie_dk, Orden, Orden_dk, Artsgruppe, Artsgruppe_dk, Slaegt_dk, Referencenavn, Reference_aar, Referencetekst, Den_danske_roedliste, Fredede_arter, Dansk, Synonymer, Synonymer_dk from allearter where 1=1  and (Rige like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Rige_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Raekke like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Raekke_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Underraekke like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Underraekke_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or 
Overklasse like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Overklasse_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Klasse like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Klasse_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Underklasse like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Underklasse_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Infraklasse like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Infraklasse_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Overorden like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Overorden_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or

Underfamilie_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Tribus like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Tribus_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Slaegt like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Slaegt_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Videnskabeligt_navn like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Dansk_navn like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Synonymer like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Synonymer_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or Artsgruppe like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%" or  
Artsgruppe_dk like "%Myoxocephalus scorpius%") order by Videnskabeligt_navn

select distinct Rige from allearter where  1=1  order by Rige asc
select distinct Raekke from allearter where  1=1  order by Raekke asc
select distinct Raekke from allearter where  1=1  and Rige="Animalia" order by Raekke asc
select distinct Rige from allearter where Raekke="Arthropoda"
select distinct Klasse from allearter where  1=1  and Rige="Animalia" and Raekke="Arthropoda" order by Klasse asc
select distinct Raekke from allearter where Klasse="Insecta"

Artsgruppe_dk like "%Tofarvet frømøl%") order by Videnskabeligt_navn

Artsgruppe_dk like "%guldbasse%") order by Videnskabeligt_navn
select distinct Familie from allearter where  1=1  order by Familie asc
select distinct Familie from allearter where Familie like "Scarabaeidae%" and  1=1  order by Familie asc
select distinct Orden from allearter where Familie="Scarabaeidae"
select distinct Klasse from allearter where Orden="Coleoptera"
select distinct Raekke from allearter where Klasse="Insecta"
select distinct Rige from allearter where Raekke="Arthropoda"

select distinct Rige from allearter where Raekke="Arthropoda"

Orden like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Orden_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Underorden like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Underorden_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Infraorden like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Infraorden_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Overfamilie like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Overfamilie_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Familie like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Familie_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Underfamilie like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or 
Underfamilie_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Tribus like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Tribus_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Slaegt like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Slaegt_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Videnskabeligt_navn like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Dansk_navn like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Synonymer like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Synonymer_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or Artsgruppe like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%" or  
Artsgruppe_dk like "%Henricia sanguinolenta%") order by Videnskabeligt_navn
select ID, Videnskabeligt_navn, Autor, Dansk_navn, Familie, Familie_dk, Orden, Orden_dk, Artsgruppe, Artsgruppe_dk, Slaegt_dk, Referencenavn, Reference_aar, Referencetekst, Den_danske_roedliste, Fredede_arter, Dansk, Synonymer, Synonymer_dk from allearter where 1=1  and (Rige like "%oncus%" or Rige_dk like "%oncus%" or Raekke like "%oncus%" or Raekke_dk like "%oncus%" or Underraekke like "%oncus%" or Underraekke_dk like "%oncus%" or 
Overklasse like "%oncus%" or Overklasse_dk like "%oncus%" or Klasse like "%oncus%" or Klasse_dk like "%oncus%" or Underklasse like "%oncus%" or Underklasse_dk like "%oncus%" or Infraklasse like "%oncus%" or Infraklasse_dk like "%oncus%" or Overorden like "%oncus%" or Overorden_dk like "%oncus%" or 
Orden like "%oncus%" or Orden_dk like "%oncus%" or Underorden like "%oncus%" or Underorden_dk like "%oncus%" or Infraorden like "%oncus%" or Infraorden_dk like "%oncus%" or Overfamilie like "%oncus%" or Overfamilie_dk like "%oncus%" or Familie like "%oncus%" or Familie_dk like "%oncus%" or Underfamilie like "%oncus%" or 
Underfamilie_dk like "%oncus%" or Tribus like "%oncus%" or Tribus_dk like "%oncus%" or Slaegt like "%oncus%" or Slaegt_dk like "%oncus%" or Videnskabeligt_navn like "%oncus%" or Dansk_navn like "%oncus%" or Synonymer like "%oncus%" or Synonymer_dk like "%oncus%" or Artsgruppe like "%oncus%" or  
Artsgruppe_dk like "%oncus%") order by Videnskabeligt_navn
